1) for getting all_pdb_ids.txt
went to PDB
clicked the hyperlink number of how many structures are in there
    (see right next to their logo on main page)
Refine Search
    Structure Features --> Link records (any)
    Structure Features --> Macromolecule Type
        Contains Protein: Yes
        Contains DNA: No
        Contains RNA: No
        Contains DNA/RNA Hybrid: No
        (ignoring cases with DNA for clarity)
select "list of select PDB IDs" from the Reports dropdown
copy and pasted IDs to a txt file
